definitions.definition: A pilot partner of another; a pilot who flies in the same wing or squadron .
A friend who accompanies one to offer (or receive ) support , especially in flirting with love interests .
A player positioned on the wing .

main_definition: A pilot partner of another; a pilot who flies in the same wing or squadron .
secondary_definitions: ( by extension ) A friend who accompanies one to offer (or receive ) support , especially in flirting with love interests .
( Australian rules football ) A player positioned on the wing .
